# Execution bout (intrinsic)

Read `01-docs/04-ops/agent-execution-bout.md` on session start.

After `pnpm agent:session-start`, use JSON `executionBout`:

1. Drain all Class **R** stories in `executionBout.stories` before bout check-in.
2. Micro-commit each story; re-run `pnpm agent:next-work` after each.
3. Short progress Status Update every `reportEveryStories` (default 2).
4. **`backlogClear` is not a stop signal** — continue while bout has Class R items.
5. Full Status Update only at bout check-in (plan complete or Class S only).
6. Forbidden: stop after one story; "Say if you want to continue"; story menus.

Planning/reconcile: `execute-roadmap` framework only — implementation uses the bout loop.
